[[!meta title="Webconverger features"]]

Latest [Firefox Web browser](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Firefox) with [HTML5
webm
video](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Media_formats_supported_by_the_audio_and_video_elements)
by default.

Most customers just need their [[homepage]] customised, however there are
further options:

* A choice of [[kiosk]] browser chrome, which helps Webconverger to the your customised homepage. There are more [[filtering]] options
* Custom [[background|artwork]] seen between sessions
* [[Kiosk_reset|blanking]] **timeout** options that reset the browser after user defined minutes of idleness/inactivity.
* [[Network_printing|printing]]
* Wired [[networking]] options such as fixing your DNS and [[wireless]] support
* [[Adobe]] Flash & PDF viewing
* [[Extensive_internationalization_support|i18n]] -  Many types of keyboard setups, such as Swiss German. Spelling support with dictionaries in many languages.
* Screen rotation and sizing options

Please see the [[API]] for a complete list of features.
